text:
..........Y-You know what!
Hinana-chan, let's study for the test together!
Ah, why did I say it like that...!

Oh, Ichikawa is here too.
Don't disturb Fukumaru's studying, okay?

You don't even know
much about Hinana-chan...!

B-But, Hinana-chan
won't be a disturbance at all!

You have to get really good grades,
or else it won't be impressive...!

What's that~?
Turning the tables, the honor student~!
